name: 311 Cases
description:
**SUMMARY**
Dataset contains SF311 cases created since 7/1/2008 with location information.
**UPDATE PROCESS**
This dataset updates nightly. New data is added around 6am pacific time.
**HOW TO USE THIS DATASET**
Download data using 'export' button to the right. For more information on this dataset, visit the [FAQ page](https://sfdigitalservices.gitbook.io/dataset-explainers/311-cases).
**Want to map the data in your neighborhood?**
Check out https://sf.connect.socrata.com/
For more information about Open311, see http://www.open311.org/.
citeAs: 311 Cases, San Francisco Open Data Portal, https://data.sfgov.org/d/vw6y-z8j6
